        <item>
            <title>广汽 AION V 正式进军香港，高达 602 公里续航＋同级最长轴距宽敞舒适</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/31/aion-v-launch-hongkong/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=aion-v-launch-hongkong</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/31/aion-v-launch-hongkong/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[duncan]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 31 Mar 2025 13:30:08 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技新闻]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Aion]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[EV]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[SUV]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[广汽]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[电动车]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1300409</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>广汽集团旗下全新 SUV 型号 AION V 今日正式登陆香港市场，搭配 400V 快充及第二代弹匣电池技术，续航力最高可达 602 公里，突破平价家庭电动车的续航距离。AION V 将推出 Premium 与 Luxury 两个版本，售价分别为 HK$218,000 及 HK$238,000 起。</p><figure id="attachment_1300435" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-1300435" style="width: 694px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1300435" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250331_144529-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250331_144529-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250331_144529-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-1300435" class="wp-caption-text"><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1300434" style="font-size: 16px;" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250331_150131-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250331_150131-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250331_150131-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></figcaption></figure><p>第二代 AION V 采用 FWD 前轮驱动，最大功率为 100kW，扭力可达 240Nm，新车提供两种规格选择，Premium 和 Luxury 版本的电池容量为 64.5kWh 及 75.26kWh 续航力分别为 505 公里及 602 公里，满足不同用户的出行需求。全系 AION V 采用磷酸铁锂（LFP）电池，支持 3C 快充技术，最快可于 16 分钟把电池由 30% 充至 80%，充电时间得以缩短。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1300429 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250331_144824-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250331_144824-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250331_144824-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><figure id="attachment_1300440" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-1300440" style="width: 694px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1300440" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250331_144801-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250331_144801-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250331_144801-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-1300440" class="wp-caption-text"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1300430 aligncenter" style="font-size: 16px;" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250331_144836-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250331_144836-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250331_144836-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></figcaption></figure><p>AION V 另一个卖点是提供多项针对家庭用户需要的设计，随车设有可电暖、通风与按摩的前座，后排椅背可向后调整至 20 度，更设有一键躺平功能，结合三层式特大车尾储物箱与车载冰箱，让驾乘体验更贴近家庭出行需要。AION V 车身尺寸为: 4605mm x 1876mm x 1686mm，长达 2775mm 的轴距为同级车中最长，后排腿部空间达 1040mm，设计宽敞，新车同时加入智能四音区语音识别系统，能根据乘客座位辨识指令，提供个人化娱乐控制。此外，AION V 配备双前气袋及双前侧气袋、前座中央气袋及两侧 2.3 米超长车侧气袋，加上标准配置的 ACC 定速巡航、AEB 主动式紧急刹车、BSD 盲点提示、ELKA 越线提示及辅助等，安全功能相当丰富。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1300431 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250331_144906-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250331_144906-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250331_144906-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1300432 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250331_144936-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250331_144936-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250331_144936-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1300433 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250331_144948_-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250331_144948_-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250331_144948_-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>内饰设计简约，配备 8.88 吋全液晶仪表和 14.6 吋中控屏幕，车门把手、空调出风口等细节采用金属装饰，提升质感。Luxury 版本配备皮质座椅，主驾座椅支持电动调节，后排座椅靠背角度可调至 137 度，并可实现 4/6 比例折叠及齐平放倒，增加实用性。​在配置上，Luxury 版较 Premium 版提供更多高级功能。​例如，Luxury 版提供冷暖冰箱、配备比利时 Premium 顶级音响系统，包括三分频设计和 8 吋重低音扬声器，提供更佳的音质和空间感。​此外，Luxury 版还可能配备感应式电动尾门、前排座椅记忆、通风加热功能，以及前排座椅按摩等高级配置，进一步提升舒适性和便利性。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1300436" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250331_144653-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250331_144653-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250331_144653-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1300437" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250331_144659-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250331_144659-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250331_144659-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1300441" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250331_144924-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250331_144924-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250331_144924-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">AION V Premium 及 Luxury 版的零售价分别为 218,000 港元及 238,000 港元，于早鸟期内订购更可享高达 10,000 港元折扣</p><p>​来源: 新闻稿</p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
